<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id796be88c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s1224"><num value="1224">§ 1224.</num><heading> Antitrust laws as affected</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No provision of this chapter shall repeal, modify, or supersede, directly or indirectly, any provision of the antitrust laws of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id796be88d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-08/ch1038/s4">Aug. 8, 1956, ch. 1038, § 4</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70/1125">70 Stat. 1125</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
